    - --- Release Notes ------------------------------------------------>

    Before I start off, let me make one thing very clear, this addon
    should only be used by advanced users who know what they are doing.
    And, please be familiar with the normal .NFO for this game, and how
    the rip works before you mess around with this addon.

    Anyway, lets start off. This addon includes all movies for CD2 of
    Grandia II. So, if you download CD1, you can master your own CD2
    rather than downloading mostly the same files over again. 

    These RAR archives contain the following files, make sure you
    UnRAR each and every single one of these:

    - SFD_ADXB.PVR
    - CG01.SFD
